{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-hub-js","path":"/bloomington","result":{"data":{"defaultLogo":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/b7ed263dd1ded402f44f1342dac6232f/6d161/sunrise-logo-padded.png","srcSet":"/static/b7ed263dd1ded402f44f1342dac6232f/94657/sunrise-logo-padded.png 38w,\n/static/b7ed263dd1ded402f44f1342dac6232f/5db04/sunrise-logo-padded.png 75w,\n/static/b7ed263dd1ded402f44f1342dac6232f/6d161/sunrise-logo-padded.png 150w,\n/static/b7ed263dd1ded402f44f1342dac6232f/7e7e9/sunrise-logo-padded.png 225w,\n/static/b7ed263dd1ded402f44f1342dac6232f/f006c/sunrise-logo-padded.png 246w","sizes":"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px"}}},"defaultHero":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.5859030837004404,"src":"/static/829bc32ea4eca8342c578da760275b34/7f945/default-hero.jpg","srcSet":"/static/829bc32ea4eca8342c578da760275b34/e2788/default-hero.jpg 360w,\n/static/829bc32ea4eca8342c578da760275b34/7d509/default-hero.jpg 720w,\n/static/829bc32ea4eca8342c578da760275b34/7f945/default-hero.jpg 1440w,\n/static/829bc32ea4eca8342c578da760275b34/47dad/default-hero.jpg 2160w,\n/static/829bc32ea4eca8342c578da760275b34/af56c/default-hero.jpg 2880w","sizes":"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px"}}},"events":{"nodes":[]},"hub":{"name":"Bloomington","about":"<p data-children-count=\"0\">We're a growing movement of young people dedicated to green jobs, and a livable future based on climate justice in Bloomington, IN.&nbsp;<br></p><p data-children-count=\"0\">*URGENT FUNDRAISING EVENT FOR COVID CRISIS IN INDIA*</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\">It is a well-established fact that there is a relationship between climate change and epidemics such as the covid-19 crisis. The steady and alarming rise in temperatures around the world has created conditions under which pathogens can and are spreading more rapidly. The compactness with which people around the world are forced to live in dense urban centers has further exacerbated susceptibility to quick and alarming disease spread. In the case of airborne diseases like covid-19, rampant air pollution is a major factor in aggravating both the spread and the vulnerability of otherwise healthy populations to risk factors.</span></p><p data-children-count=\"0\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-07d87b26-7fff-0341-f32b-37943400e9d7\"><br><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\">At Sunrise, we strongly believe that given the interconnectedness of the globalized world we live in, addressing health and climate crises in the global South is imperative to combating climate change and creating a livable future for us all. The </span><a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2020/world/asia/india-coronavirus-cases.html\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration-skip: none; vertical-align: baseline;\">ongoing COVID crisis in India</span></a><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\"> in particular has been alarming, with over 200,000 deaths, and over 18 million cases reported so far. Experts say that statistics on deaths and number of cases are far undercounted, and that the numbers will tragically continue to soar in the coming weeks. In the face of such human tragedy and loss, we ask you to consider making a donation of any amount to any of the following mutual aid fundraisers. We give you two options: either you can donate to the fundraiser of your choice directly, or you can donate to Sunrise and we will contribute to the most urgent fundraisers on your behalf. </span></span><br></p>","email":"sunrisebloomington@gmail.com","website":"https://forms.gle/K235U9nv539ynb9EA","twitter":"https://twitter.com/SunriseBTown","facebook":"https://www.facebook.com/Sunrise-Bloomington-102230905231663","instagram":"https://www.instagram.com/sunrise_bloomington/","signup":"https://forms.gle/zdH2DyS46L7nbd1s7","donations":"https://secure.actblue.com/donate/sunrisebloomington","websiteText":"FUNDRAISER FOR COVID-19 CRISIS IN INDIA","logo":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/1ee2905a236dd742dc804e550878be32/6d161/logo_1612651802.png.png","srcSet":"/static/1ee2905a236dd742dc804e550878be32/94657/logo_1612651802.png.png 38w,\n/static/1ee2905a236dd742dc804e550878be32/5db04/logo_1612651802.png.png 75w,\n/static/1ee2905a236dd742dc804e550878be32/6d161/logo_1612651802.png.png 150w,\n/static/1ee2905a236dd742dc804e550878be32/7e7e9/logo_1612651802.png.png 225w,\n/static/1ee2905a236dd742dc804e550878be32/630fb/logo_1612651802.png.png 300w,\n/static/1ee2905a236dd742dc804e550878be32/46604/logo_1612651802.png.png 500w","sizes":"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px"}}},"hero":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.5,"src":"/static/d36a354a51dc5f8b7fc0448844f54a26/7f945/hero_1612651802.jpg.jpg","srcSet":"/static/d36a354a51dc5f8b7fc0448844f54a26/e2788/hero_1612651802.jpg.jpg 360w,\n/static/d36a354a51dc5f8b7fc0448844f54a26/7d509/hero_1612651802.jpg.jpg 720w,\n/static/d36a354a51dc5f8b7fc0448844f54a26/7f945/hero_1612651802.jpg.jpg 1440w,\n/static/d36a354a51dc5f8b7fc0448844f54a26/47dad/hero_1612651802.jpg.jpg 2160w,\n/static/d36a354a51dc5f8b7fc0448844f54a26/af56c/hero_1612651802.jpg.jpg 2880w,\n/static/d36a354a51dc5f8b7fc0448844f54a26/c128d/hero_1612651802.jpg.jpg 5760w","sizes":"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px"}}},"documents":[]}},"pageContext":{"id":"e365e9eb-6f1b-5efa-9ded-494d6d9b09a9"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1219170061","3649515864"]}